@node MAIN
@title "The Dominion War 2"
==============================================================================
                             The Dominion War 2
==============================================================================
         A scenario for the game "-Star_Trek-" by Frank Mathieson
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

+++ UNITED FEDERATION OF PLANETS
+++ STARFLEET HEADQUARTERS
+++ STARDATE 50996.5
+++ ADMIRAL CONSIERGE

Dear Captain F. MILLER,

a large attack fleet of 50 Jem'Hadar and Cardassian warships is
threatening the Federation's starbases. In addition, a Borg Cube has
been sighted.

I give you the command over the Galaxy class ship USS SAVANNAH
(NCC-1752) in order to join the Federation fleet defending the
Federation against the mighty Dominion and the Borg.

It's up to you and the 5 other Federation ships to save the last
dozen starbases left after the last bloody war against the Dominion.

Good luck, Captain!
==============================================================================
