@node SCENARIOOVERVIEW
@title "What is in this scenario?"

@{b}OVERVIEW@{ub}

Estimated difficulty: Medium
Solvable with unregistered version: Yes (tested)

This scenario is thought for people who find the standard game and
the "DominionWar" scenario provided with it too easy, but
"BorgInvasion" and "Madness" too hard. In addition, it takes a little
more time to finish, but since you have a nice number of starbases
and Federation ships at your side, you have some time to find a good
strategy. I think you have a very fair chance to win this one...
_____________________________________________________________________

ENEMY UNITS

25x Cardassian Cruiser (GALOR CLASS)           300
25x Dominion Warship (JEM'HADAR CLASS)         375
 1x Borg Cube                                 2200
_____________________________________________________________________

YOUR UNITS

12x Starbase
USS CAIRO (NCC-42136, EXCELSIOR CLASS)         300
USS GORKON (NCC-50446, EXCELSIOR CLASS)        250
USS ENTERPRISE (NCC-1701-E, SOVEREIGN CLASS)   325
USS DEFIANT (NX-74205, DEFIANT CLASS)          350
USS BOZEMAN (NCC-1941, SOYUZ CLASS)            180
